Package Implementation

Class GameProgress

java.lang.Object
Implementation.DataManager
Implementation.GameProgress
public class GameProgress extends Implementation.DataManager
The GameProgress class extends DataManager to provide methods for retrieving and updating game progress data from a CSV file. This class manages player progression, including level, experience, quests completed, and earned badges.
